      <body>
         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Redaction der Mittheilungen ¶ aus Justus Perthes geographischer Anstalt. ¶ Gotha, ¶  ¶ 8. January ¶  ¶ 18 ¶ 70. ¶ My Dear Friend, ¶  ¶ Allow me to introduce to you Mr. Hugo Strong, the son of the Cons...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">70.01.08</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From August Petermann</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">RB MSS M199, Library, Royal Botanic Gardens Melbourne.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="formtext" style="color: #2F5496; ">Redaction der Mittheilungen</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="formtext" style="color: #2F5496; ">aus Justus Perthes geographischer Anstalt.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="formtext" style="color: #2F5496; ">Gotha,</seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>8. January<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="formtext" style="color: #2F5496; ">18</seg>70.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">My Dear Friend,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Allow me to introduce to you Mr. Hugo Strong, the son of the Consul-General Mr. F. Strong at Hamburg, an esteemed friend of mine, and one of the best friends of German Geographers and Scientific men, who for many years has warmly encouraged all German endeavours and undertakings, and who therefore will be sure to receive the sympathy of so great a patriot as yourself and in his position as the<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">Humboldt of Australia</hi>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>See Home (1998).</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>will receive these lines from the hands of his son.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">With the sincerest attachments</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>ever your devoted</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>A Petermann</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">You will have received various letters and communications sent you during the last months.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Chev. Dr. F. von Müller, F.R.G. &amp; L.S.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Director of the Botanical Garden</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Melbourne<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>MS annotation by M: 'Upper Footscray.' [Vic]. Presumably where<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Strong was staying.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
         </div>
